{
  "id": "69a614af2d2c3e49e6be6840",
  "title": "プログラミングで解決したい",
  "created": 1772491990,
  "updated": 1772681951,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a614af2d2c3e49e6be6840",
      "text": "プログラミングで解決したい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491990,
      "updated": 1772491990
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614e1000000000002bb25",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772492001,
      "updated": 1772492001
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614e1000000000002bb26",
      "text": "[ふーことましろとひよりの会話]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772492001,
      "updated": 1772492016
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614ee000000000002bb27",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772492014,
      "updated": 1772492014
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d6000000000002ba60",
      "text": "――放課後の教室。窓の外はゆるく夕焼け。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491990,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba61",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba62",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]（進行係）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba63",
      "text": "ねえねえ二人とも！ 今日のテーマいくよー！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba64",
      "text": "「プログラミングで解決したい」！ どーん！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba65",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba66",
      "text": "最近さ、なんかもう、人生のバグ多くね？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba67",
      "text": "だったらコードで直せばよくね？って思ったわけ。はい拍手〜。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba68",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba69",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba6a",
      "text": "ふふ、ふーこらしい発想ね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba6b",
      "text": "でも素敵だと思うわ。「困った」を自分で仕組みにして解決するって、とても前向きだもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba6c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba6d",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba6e",
      "text": "発想としては合理的。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba6f",
      "text": "プログラミングは「作業を自動化する技術」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba70",
      "text": "繰り返し発生する問題には特に有効。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba71",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba72",
      "text": "[** まず何を解決したい？]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba73",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba74",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba75",
      "text": "わたし？ 宿題の[進捗管理]！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772681936
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba76",
      "text": "「あ、やべ今日提出じゃん」って毎回なるの、完全に仕様バグなんだが？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba77",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba78",
      "text": "なんかさ、「未来のわたしに通知するアプリ」ほしい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba79",
      "text": "しかも強制力あるやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba7a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba7b",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba7c",
      "text": "通知だけでは行動変容は弱い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba7d",
      "text": "行動経済学的には「[即時フィードバック]」と「[損失回避]」を組み合わせると効果が上がる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772681951
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba7e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba7f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba80",
      "text": "ちょ、急にむずワードきた。翻訳して？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba81",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba82",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba83",
      "text": "「すぐ結果が返ってくる仕組み」と",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba84",
      "text": "「やらないと損する仕組み」を入れろ、ということ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba85",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba86",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba87",
      "text": "あー、なるほど。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba88",
      "text": "宿題やらなかったら、推しの画像が1日見られなくなるとか？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba89",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba8a",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba8b",
      "text": "それはちょっとつらいわね……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba8c",
      "text": "でも「やったら褒めてくれる」仕組みのほうが、私は好きだな。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba8d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba8e",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba8f",
      "text": "報酬型設計。ポジティブ強化。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba90",
      "text": "長期的にはそちらが安定する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba91",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba92",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba93",
      "text": "よし決まり！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba94",
      "text": "「宿題やると推しが褒めてくれるアプリ」作ろう。神では？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba95",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba96",
      "text": "[** プログラミングって万能？]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba97",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba98",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba99",
      "text": "でもね、ふーこ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba9a",
      "text": "全部をプログラムで解決しようとすると、少し苦しくならない？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba9b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba9c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba9d",
      "text": "え、なんで？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba9e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002ba9f",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baa0",
      "text": "人の気持ちや迷いは、単純なルールでは割り切れないこともあるでしょう？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baa1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baa2",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baa3",
      "text": "同意。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baa4",
      "text": "プログラミングは「明確なルールがある問題」に強い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baa5",
      "text": "曖昧な問題は、設計が難しい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baa6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baa7",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baa8",
      "text": "つまり？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baa9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baaa",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baab",
      "text": "「数学の計算」は得意。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baac",
      "text": "「なんかやる気出ない」は苦手。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baae",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baaf",
      "text": "あーーー。それはガチ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bab0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bab1",
      "text": "[** それでも作りたい理由]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bab2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bab3",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bab4",
      "text": "でもさ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bab5",
      "text": "ぐちゃぐちゃな問題を、ちょっとでも整理できたら気持ちよくない？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bab6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bab7",
      "text": "なんか「世界をわかりやすくする」感じ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bab8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bab9",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baba",
      "text": "それはとても素敵ね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002babb",
      "text": "混乱しているものを、順番に並べていく。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002babc",
      "text": "それだけで心が軽くなること、あるもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002babd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002babe",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002babf",
      "text": "プログラミングは「思考の外部化」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bac0",
      "text": "頭の中の手順を、紙に書くように外へ出す行為。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bac1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bac2",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bac3",
      "text": "おお、かっこいい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bac4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bac5",
      "text": "つまりさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bac6",
      "text": "「わたしの脳みそを拡張するツール」ってこと？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bac7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bac8",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bac9",
      "text": "概ね正しい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bacb",
      "text": "[** それぞれの「解決したい」]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bacc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bacd",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bace",
      "text": "私はね……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bacf",
      "text": "学校のプリント管理を自動化したいな。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bad0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bad1",
      "text": "どこに何があるか、いつも探してしまうの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bad2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bad3",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bad4",
      "text": "あーわかる！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bad5",
      "text": "「あの紙どこいった問題」永遠のバグ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bad6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bad7",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bad8",
      "text": "画像認識＋OCR。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bad9",
      "text": "プリントを撮影すれば、文字を読み取って分類可能。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bada",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002badb",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002badc",
      "text": "ちょ、未来すぎる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002badd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bade",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002badf",
      "text": "ふふ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bae0",
      "text": "でも、そういう仕組みがあれば安心ね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bae1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bae2",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bae3",
      "text": "私は、勉強の理解度を数値化したい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bae4",
      "text": "「なんとなくわかった」を排除する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bae5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bae6",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bae7",
      "text": "出た、理詰めモード。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bae8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bae9",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baea",
      "text": "曖昧な自己評価は誤差が大きい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baeb",
      "text": "テスト生成プログラムを作れば、客観的に測定できる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baec",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baed",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baee",
      "text": "ひよりらしいわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baef",
      "text": "でも、その真面目さ、とても素敵よ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baf0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baf1",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baf2",
      "text": "……ありがとう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baf3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baf4",
      "text": "[** 結論っぽいもの]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baf5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baf6",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]（まとめモード）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baf7",
      "text": "はい！ 今日の気づき！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baf8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baf9",
      "text": " プログラミングは「繰り返す問題」に強い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bafa",
      "text": " 気持ち全部は直せないけど、整理はできる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bafb",
      "text": " 自分の弱点を補助するツールになる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bafc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bafd",
      "text": "って感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bafe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002baff",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb00",
      "text": "妥当なまとめ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb01",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb02",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb03",
      "text": "うん、とてもわかりやすいわ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb04",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb05",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb06",
      "text": "じゃあ決定！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb07",
      "text": "わたしたち、「自分専用の最強サポートアプリ」作る部、結成な！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb08",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb09",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb0a",
      "text": "まず[要件定義]から。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772506042
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb0b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb0c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb0d",
      "text": "出たーーー。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb0e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb0f",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb10",
      "text": "ふふ、でもそれが第一歩ね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb11",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb12",
      "text": "――夕焼けがゆっくりと紫に変わる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb13",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb14",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb15",
      "text": "ねえ、もしさ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb16",
      "text": "プログラミングで世界をちょっとでもラクにできるなら、やらない理由なくない？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb17",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb18",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb19",
      "text": "可能性があるなら、試す価値はある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb1a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb1b",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb1c",
      "text": "そうね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb1d",
      "text": "無理に全部を解決しなくてもいい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb1e",
      "text": "でも、少し楽にすることはできるもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb1f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb20",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb21",
      "text": "よし、まずは宿題アプリからだな。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb22",
      "text": "未来のわたし、覚悟しとけよ〜。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb23",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    },
    {
      "id": "69a614d7000000000002bb24",
      "text": "三人の笑い声が、静かな教室にゆるく溶けていった。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491991,
      "updated": 1772491991
    }
  ]
}